Kanye West obviously isn’t taking any chances with his health. Kim Kardashian rushed her husband Kanye West to hospital over the weekend, according to reports in the US. It seems that he suffered from a severe case of the flu and that’s why the visit to the hospital was necessary. The Keeping Up With The Kardashians star was so worried about her husband after he came down with a bad flu that she took him to the emergency room of West Hills Hospital, in the San Fernando Valley, reports TMZ. [Ad] It was reported that his condition got worse and that’s why doctors needed to treat him with some Rx. West could be prescribed antibiotics. However, the trip to the Los Angeles-area hospital was a quick one, with the couple checking out as quickly as they checked in. [Ad unit=2]